Applying Chocolate Caramel Hair Color with Metal Detox

We talk about a chocolate caramel hair color that the client has had before. I’ll use a metal detox to protect the hair and a 1:1 ratio of 6 stock 74 vela with 30 volume. I’ll apply the color to the length, leaving the roots, and use 6 74 and 6 base for gray coverage with 30 volume. I’ll start at the roots and let it process for 30-35 minutes. The color will look great in indoor light and change completely when taken outside.
